<section id="res_resourceItemRef">
    <title>resourceItemRef</title>
    <para>Specifies a reference to an associated <olink targetdoc="../../elements/resourcedata/resourceItem.xml" targetptr="res_resourceItem"><code>&lt;resourceItem></code></olink> element located at the <olink targetdoc="../../elements/structural/file.xml" targetptr="file"><code>&lt;file></code></olink> level.</para>
    <para><emphasis>Contains:</emphasis></para>
    <simplelist>
        <member>This element is always empty.</member>
    </simplelist>
    <para><emphasis>Attributes:</emphasis></para>
    <simplelist>
      <member>- <olink targetdoc="../../attributes/resourceData/res_id.xml" targetptr="res_id"><code>id</code></olink>, <glossterm>optional</glossterm></member>
      <member>- <olink targetdoc="../../attributes/resourceData/res_ref.xml" targetptr="res_ref"><code>ref</code></olink>, <glossterm>required</glossterm></member>
      <member>- attributes from other namespaces, <glossterm>optional</glossterm></member>
    </simplelist>

  <itemizedlist>
    <title>Constraints</title>

    <listitem>
      <para>The value of the <glossterm>optional</glossterm> <olink targetdoc="../../attributes/resourceData/res_id.xml" targetptr="res_id">id</olink> attribute
        <glossterm>must</glossterm> be unique among all <olink targetdoc="../../elements/resourceData/resourceItem.xml" targetptr="res_resourceItem"><code>&lt;resourceItem></code></olink>
        and <olink targetdoc="../../elements/resourceData/resourceItemRef.xml" targetptr="res_resourceItemRef"><code>&lt;resourceItemRef></code></olink>
        elements of the enclosing <olink targetdoc="../../elements/resourceData/resourceData.xml" targetptr="res_resourceData"><code>&lt;resourceData></code></olink> element.</para>
    </listitem>
    
  </itemizedlist>
    <itemizedlist>
      <title>Processing Requirements</title>
      
    <listitem>
      <para><firstterm>Modifiers</firstterm>
        <glossterm>must</glossterm> remove <olink
          targetdoc="../../elements/resourceData/resourceItemRef.xml"
          targetptr="res_resourceItemRef"><code>&lt;resourceItemRef></code></olink> when removing
        the referenced <olink targetdoc="../../elements/resourceData/resourcItem.xml"
          targetptr="res_resourceItem"><code>&lt;resourceItem></code></olink>.</para>
    </listitem>
    
  </itemizedlist>
</section>
